      <title>法国将堕胎权写入国家宪法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/france-enshrines-right-to-seek-an-abortion-in-its-constitution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国将在宪法中规定妇女寻求堕胎的权利，此举是为了回应美国限制堕胎的做法。]]></description>
